Alembic Database Migrations
============================

This directory contains Alembic migration scripts for the Aprep AI Agent System.

## Usage

### Create a new migration

```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations

```bash
# Upgrade to latest
alembic upgrade head

# Upgrade by 1 version
alembic upgrade +1

# Downgrade by 1 version
alembic downgrade -1
```

### Check current version

```bash
alembic current
```

### View migration history

```bash
alembic history
```

## Initial Setup

The initial migration creates all tables from the SQLAlchemy models.

To apply the initial schema:

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

## Database URL

The database URL is configured in `.env`:

```
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:port/database
```

## Notes

- Always review auto-generated migrations before applying
- Test migrations in development before production
- Keep migrations in version control
